{{vgname|謂何|en=Tell Me Why}}是一款由[[Dontnod_Entertainment|Dontnod Entertainment]]開發並由[[Xbox遊戲工作室|Xbox遊戲工作室]]發行在[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]與[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]平台上的章節性[[冒險遊戲|冒險遊戲]]，總共有三個章節，先後於2020年8月和9月公開，並在之後合併成捆綁版發售。

《謂何》在發行後得到評論家們大致良好的評價，並分別在[[Gamescom|Gamescom]]大獎和[[遊戲大獎|遊戲大獎]]上獲提名最佳Microsoft Xbox遊戲和最具影響力遊戲，最終雙雙獲獎。

== 遊戲玩法 ==
在《謂何》中，玩家會與[[龍鳳胎|雙胞胎]]泰勒（Tyler）和艾莉森（Alyson）一起回到其位於[[阿拉斯加州|阿拉斯加州]]德洛斯克羅辛（Delos Crossing）的舊屋，試圖了解發生在兩位身上的異象以及他們對此的記憶，之後玩家便要根據自己看過的雙胞胎的過去事件，作出會影響遊戲結果的決定<ref name="ign announce">{{cite web | url = https://www.ign.com/articles/2019/11/14/tell-me-why-is-the-new-episodic-game-from-life-is-strange-studio | title = Tell Me Why Is the New Episodic Game from Life Is Strange Studio | first = Adam | last = Bankhurst | date = 2019-11-14 | accessdate = 2019-11-14 | work = [[IGN|IGN]] | archive-date = 2019-11-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191114231908/https://www.ign.com/articles/2019/11/14/tell-me-why-is-the-new-episodic-game-from-life-is-strange-studio | dead-url = no }}</ref>。《謂何》還包含對[[特林吉特人|特林吉特]]人的探索，並包括幾個特林吉特人角色<ref name="GLAAD">{{cite web|last=Farokhmanesh|first=Megan|date=2019-11-14|title=Life is Strange developer unveils new mystery game, Tell Me Why|url=https://www.theverge.com/entertainment/2019/11/14/20964923/life-is-strange-tell-me-why-dontnod-xbox-pc|accessdate=2019-11-14|work=[[The_Verge|The Verge]]|archive-date=2020-01-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200109230424/https://www.theverge.com/entertainment/2019/11/14/20964923/life-is-strange-tell-me-why-dontnod-xbox-pc|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Van Allen|first=Eric|date=2019-11-14|title=Life is Strange Developer's New Game Will Explore Memories and the Trans Experience Through Twins|url=https://www.usgamer.net/articles/life-is-strange-developers-new-game-will-explore-memories-and-the-trans-experience-through-twins|accessdate=2019-11-14|work=USGamer|archive-date=2019-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191114231912/https://www.usgamer.net/articles/life-is-strange-developers-new-game-will-explore-memories-and-the-trans-experience-through-twins|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

《謂何》的男主角泰勒·羅南（Tyler Ronan）是所有主要工作室製作的遊戲中第一個可玩變性人角色，Dontnod還與[[GLAAD|GLAAD]]合作，務求使該角色成為「變性經歷的真實代表」<ref name="GLAAD"/>。羅南的配音員奧古斯特·艾登·布萊克（August Aiden Black）本身亦是一位[[跨性別|跨性別]]男性<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://stevivor.com/news/tell-my-why-transgender-lead-voice-actor-august-black/|title=Tell Me Why's transgender lead is voiced by a transgender male|date=2020-02-21|first=Steve|last=Wright|work=stevivor|accessdate=2020-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210120230511/https://stevivor.com/news/tell-my-why-transgender-lead-voice-actor-august-black/|archive-date=2021-01-20|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.vg247.com/2020/02/18/meet-tyler-ronan-first-transgender-triple-video-game-protagonist/|title=Meet Tyler Ronan, the first transgender triple-A video game protagonist|date=2020-02-18|first=Stacey|last=Henley|work=[[VG247|VG247]]|accessdate=2020-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210226121316/https://www.vg247.com/2020/02/18/meet-tyler-ronan-first-transgender-triple-video-game-protagonist/|archive-date=2021-02-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

== 開發 ==
《謂何》在2019年11月14日於倫敦[[微軟|微軟]]Xbox活動上首次公開開發中的消息，Dontnod表示鑑於《[[奇妙人生|奇妙人生]]》被批評其章節上架時間過疏的關係，他們會致力於在2020年中期內發布《謂何》的所有章節<ref name="ign announce"/>。

《謂何》為繼2013年的《[[記憶駭客|記憶駭客]]》，Dontnod七年來第一款支援其他語言配音的遊戲，但由於[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]的影響，其法語、德語、[[墨西哥西班牙語|墨西哥西班牙語]]和[[巴西葡萄牙語|巴西葡萄牙語]]配音版本的錄音被推遲，因此遊戲僅提供了不同語言的字幕<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.tellmewhygame.com/faq/|title=FAQ Tell Me Why|accessdate=2020-08-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210309193930/https://www.tellmewhygame.com/faq/|archive-date=2021-03-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《謂何》的配音版本後來於2020年10月31日發行<ref>{{cite web |last1=Sirio |first1=Paolo |title=Tell Me Why mantiene la promessa: tutti i doppiatori di Tyler sono trans |url=https://www.spaziogames.it/tell-me-why-mantiene-la-promessa-tutti-i-doppiatori-di-tyler-sono-trans/ |website=SpazioGames |language=it |date=2020-10-31 |access-date=2021-01-20 |archive-date=2020-11-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201125132156/https://www.spaziogames.it/tell-me-why-mantiene-la-promessa-tutti-i-doppiatori-di-tyler-sono-trans/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

